  <p class="sec-body" id="weatherNote" style="margin-bottom:0">Mizoram experiences monsoon (May-September), pleasant autumn (October-November), cool winter (December-February) and warm spring (March-April). October to May offers ideal weather with clear skies, comfortable temperatures and excellent visibility for exploring hills and villages.</p>
